 Create folder **policies/**  
 Create file **developer-policy.json**  
 Paste *ONLY this*

   json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowEC2StartStop",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "ec2:StartInstances",
        "ec2:StopInstances",
        "ec2:DescribeInstances"
      ],
      "Resource": "*"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "DenyEC2Terminate",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Action": "ec2:TerminateInstances",
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}
